data.description: Discover A Private Retreat Nestled In Tranquil Malabar On 8.39 Acres That Seamlessly Combines Elegance & Comfort. The Kitchen Boasts A Granite Island w/ Dual Sinks & Incredible Views. The Sunlit Dining Room Is Surrounded By Windows, & The Family Room Features A Gas Fireplace Extending To An Outdoor Hearth. A Luxurious Master Suite Graces The Main Floor w/ A  Stunning Master Closet. Two Bedrooms & A Spacious Loft/ Flex Space Upstairs. Balconies Adorn Both Front & Back. Entertain On Your Spacious Lanai w/ Your Summer Kitchen Overlooking Your Sparkling Heated Salt Water Pool & Spa. Enjoy A Game Of Basketball On Your Full Court. 6 Car Carport For All Your Vehicles & ...Not One But Two Sheds For Storage. Hurry & Schedule Your Showing Today To See This One Of A Kind Property!
